<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.1">
<l>vaṇṭuṇu naṟumala riṇṭaikoṇṭu</l>
<l>paṇṭainam viṉaikeṭa veṉṟaṭimēl</l>
<l>toṇṭaru mamararum paṇiyaniṉṟaṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṭamo ṭakaliṭa maḷantavaṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who measured [these] wide lands and the heavens,</l>
<l>Standing there while devotees and immortals worship at [your] feet,</l>
<l>Bearing garlands of fragrant flowers where bees sip,</l>
<l>Saying [for you] to destroy our past karma,</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
